# UI (Orbix)

## Brand (app/globals.css)

- Light primary: teal `--brand-accent` (#00d1b2) via `bg-primary`
- Dark primary: pink `--brand-accent-alt` (#f06292) — do not force teal CTAs in dark mode
- Surfaces: semantic tokens only (`bg-background`, `bg-card`, `bg-muted`, `text-foreground`, `text-muted-foreground`, `border-border`)

## Always

- shadcn/ui for Button, Card, Dialog, Sheet, Table, Input, ToggleGroup, etc.
- Spacing scale: **4, 6, 8, 12, 16, 24, 32** (dense UI may use 48, 64)
- Radius: `rounded-xl` / `rounded-2xl`; pills & nav `rounded-full`; Swap shell `rounded-[24px]`–`[28px]`
- Width: `max-w-[480px]` (swap/forms), `max-w-6xl` (marketing/docs); padding `px-4 sm:px-6`
- Support dark mode with `dark:` + CSS variables
- Reuse patterns from: `home-view.tsx`, `swap-card.tsx`, `factory-create-card.tsx`, `site-layout.tsx`
- Exchange UI polish: `@design-system` + domain skills (`trading-page`, `forms`, …)

## Never

- Hardcode hex/rgb in TSX when tokens exist
- Add MUI, Ant Design, Chakra, or new CSS-in-JS libraries without approval
- Custom `components/ui/*` duplicates of shadcn blocks
- Generic “AI purple” gradients or unrelated font stacks
- Per-page heavy backgrounds — use `SiteLayout` grid/grain
